OL,3,CEight fire engines and dozens of
OL,4,Cfirefighters attend Hackney fire
OL,6,FEight fire engines and 60 firefighters
OL,7,Fare attending a fire in Hackney,
OL,8,FLondon.
OL,10,FA static caravan and two cars are
OL,11,Falight, as well as part of a grass
OL,12,Fembankment, according to London Fire
OL,13,FBrigade.
OL,15,FMore than 20 calls were made to
OL,16,Femergency services from around 6pm in
OL,17,Fresponse to the fire, and crews from
OL,18,FHomerton, Leyton, Whitechapel and
OL,19,Fsurrounding fire stations are
OL,20,Fattending the scene.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/2
